title: Drew Brees' Journey, The Cleveland Browns Drama And The Herd Hierarchy
itunes:title: Drew Brees' Journey, The Cleveland Browns Drama And The Herd Hierarchy
description:
Colin talks about the journey of Drew Brees and what the greats have to deal with to succeed, the continuing drama of the Browns, one major advantage Drew Brees has over Tom Brady going forward, and his new Herd Hierarchy.

Guests include Geoff Schwartz, Peter King, Zach Strief, and LaVar Arrington.
